<% content_for :header do %>
  User repository accessible by <%= @business.name %> owner
<% end %>

<%= render Mail::HeaderTitleComponent.new \
  title: "User repository accessible by #{@unlocked_by}", avatar_plus_avatar: [@business, @user] %>

Hi <strong><%= @user.display_login %></strong>,

<%= render(Mail::SpacerComponent.new) %>

Your <strong><%= @repo_name %></strong> user repository can now be accessed by an owner of your enterprise,
<%= @business.name %>.
The owner, <strong><%= @unlocked_by %></strong>, will be able to access your repository for up to
<%= @access_duration.inspect %>.

<%= render(Mail::SpacerComponent.new) %>

Repositories created with an enterprise managed user account may be subject to enterprise-wide audits and review at the enterprise owner's discretion.
If you would like more information or believe this action has been taken in error, please contact an enterprise owner.

<% content_for :footer_text do %>
  You are receiving this email because an owner of the <%= @business.name %> enterprise has been granted temporary
  access to your enterprise managed user repository.
<% end %>
